<problem id="fs-id1501775">
<para id="fs-id1414274">Graph the equation by plotting points: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1530206"><para id="fs-id1171104019689"><newline/>
<media id="fs-id1601285" alt="The graph shows the x y-coordinate plane. The x and y-axis each run from -12 to 12. A line passes through the points “ordered pair 0, 0” and “ordered pair 1, -4”.">
