<media id="fs-id1342577" alt="The graph shows the x y-coordinate plane. The x and y-axis each run from -7 to 7. A line passes through three labeled points, “ordered pair 0, 3”, “ordered pair 2, 4”, and ordered pair 4, 5”. The line is labeled y = 1 over 2 x + 3.">
